AB  - With the development of gantry crane in the direction of large scale, high parameter and high speed, more and more demands are raised for its reliability and safety. The safety monitoring system for large gantry crane is designed and developed in this paper, which can monitor 10 parameters, such as lifting capacity, lifting height\descent depth, traveling distance, crane running deviation, operation instructions and working time, and 6 states, such as brake state of lifting mechanism, wind resistant and anti slip state in real-Time. The system has been installed on the large gantry crane of shipbuilding enterprises. And it is running steadily and easy to operate. The comprehensive error of this system is less than 5%. The development of this system provides an effective means to ensure the long-Term stable operation of gantry crane.
