AB  - In view of the current domestic large crane industry over-reliance on operator experience, do not have environmental recognition and intelligent control functions and other problems. In this paper, the use of digital twin technology can be a good solution to the physical space and information space blend with each other, and through the mapping of information in the virtual space to help physical entities better data monitoring and help operators to make decisions and other advantages, developed based on digital twin crawler crane simulation system. Through the 3D modeling of the crane and the model reduction, and then import game engine to complete the development of the simulation platform. The results show that the system runs stably and provides a new method for troubleshooting and danger elimination of crawler crane hoisting in complex environment. © 2022 IEEE.
